name: Glitter mirror disco ball miniature adjustable ring
description:
Add a lil' funk to your fingers with this fun 70's inspired glittery disco mirror ball on an adjustable ring band! ;)
It catches the light and scatters it all over the room with pretty crystal colors of green purple pinks and blues etc...
Its really a fun little ring and sure to be a conversation starter! :) 

It is made from real mirror pieces and sits on an adjustable ring base, so it should fit most ring sizes.

name: Arrow Chevron rose armour metal full finger long adjustable double ring
description:
This pretty ring should fit most fingers, because it it adjustable.
It has a cute filigree arrow pendant and vintage decorative rose pendant, surrounded by ringlets with transparent crystal beads to create sparkle.. you know how we girls love to sparkle! :)

What you need to know:
1. Comfort- its lightweight, but does take some getting used to all the dangles and angles.
2. Size is adjustable to fit most finger shapes and sizes.
3. Made from Silver plated metal.

name: Guitar pick plectrum holder music ring
description:
Want to play but forgot your picks? Boyfriend/husband lost his? Pull this baby out and impress everyone with your pick storage..on hand! ;)

It is backed by soft felt material and has a tiny red ribbon rose with green leaves.

As far as I know, I am the only one who makes these, so they are unique, and are as aesthetically pleasing as they are functional!

It comes with ONE FREE plectrum/pick!

Its on a silver plated adjustable band which should fit most ring sizes.

name: Butterfly glass glitter ball globe statement ring
description:
Cute idea for a hen night or dress up party or fantasy photo shoot!
This listing is for one delicate glass fantasy kawaii butterfly ring.
All come with white butterflies.

What you need to know:
* It is made from real glass
* Adjustable rings- One size fits all.
* To take care at home: wipe with a damp microfiber cloth and let dry.

name: Hemmatite and jet black gothic burlesque bracelet
description:
This beautiful Hematite (natural grey stone) bracelet is really pretty!

Great for a special event and can even be worn for casual looks.
Comes with a lobster clasp and extender chain, so oi should fit most wrist sizes and shapes.
